snippet.title: Best VGM 2040 - Super Mario 3D World - Sprawling Savanna
snippet.description:
See also:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii U
Super Mario 3D World (2013)
Sprawling Savanna
Mahito Yokota, Toru Minegishi, Yasuaki Iwata & Koji Kondo
